Note on derivative content:

`apu650-probe/src/uapi.rs` is a structural Rust transcription of the
`mdw_ioctl.h` header from MediaTek's mtk-apusys-driver tree (GPL-2.0). It
mirrors public ABI definitions for interoperability purposes; no kernel code
is linked or redistributed.

The MediaTek Genio SDK (`ncc-tflite`, `neuronrt`, `libneuron*.so`, etc.) is
NOT covered by this license and is NOT included in this repository. It is
licensed separately by MediaTek under their developer-portal EULA. See
`docs/DLA.md` for the lawful way to obtain it.
